- BECAUSE WHY?

504
00:20:26,208 --> 00:20:28,125
BE CAREFUL.

505
00:20:28,208 --> 00:20:30,291
- BECAUSE I DON'T HAVE TO.

506
00:20:30,375 --> 00:20:32,958
